`,o.jsx(t.p,{children:"Set in the chaos of Kathmandu's streets, Bluff Momo is all about deception. You can pretend to be any character to use their power — like claiming to be the Chor to steal someone's momo. But if someone calls your bluff and you were lying, you lose cards. If you were telling the truth, they lose cards instead."}),`
